msgid "Save page draft"
msgstr "Simpan draf halaman"

msgid ""
"Creates a new draft version of the page with the current element state.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only\n"
"\n"
"    **Request body (optional):**\n"
"    - description: Change description for this draft"
msgstr ""
"Membuat versi draf baru dari halaman dengan status elemen saat ini.\n"
"\n"
"**Otorisasi:** Hanya staf\n"
"\n"
"**Badan permintaan (opsional):**\n"
"- deskripsi: Ubah deskripsi untuk draf ini"

msgid "Draft saved with version ID and number"
msgstr "Draft disimpan dengan ID versi dan nomor"

msgid "Publish page"
msgstr "Terbitkan halaman"

msgid ""
"Publishes the current draft version of a page, making it live.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only\n"
"\n"
"    **Request body (optional):**\n"
"    - notes: Publish notes for the history log"
msgstr ""
"Menerbitkan versi draf saat ini dari halaman, sehingga menjadi live.\n"
"\n"
"**Otorisasi:** Hanya staf\n"
"\n"
"**Badan permintaan (opsional):**\n"
"- catatan: Catatan penerbitan untuk log sejarah"

msgid "Page published with version details"
msgstr "Halaman diterbitkan dengan detail versi"

msgid "Get page versions"
msgstr "Dapatkan versi halaman"

msgid ""
"Returns all versions of a page for the version history panel.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only"
msgstr ""
"Mengembalikan semua versi halaman untuk panel sejarah versi.\n"
"\n"
"**Autentikasi:** Hanya staf"

msgid "List of page versions with metadata"
msgstr "Daftar versi halaman dengan metadata"

msgid "Get published page by slug"
msgstr "Dapatkan halaman terbit berdasarkan slug"

msgid ""
"Get published page content by slug. Public endpoint for headless frontends. "
"Only returns published pages. Includes SEO metadata and page elements."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan konten halaman yang diterbitkan berdasarkan slug. Titik akhir umum "
"untuk frontend headless. Hanya mengembalikan halaman yang diterbitkan. "
"Termasuk metadata SEO dan elemen halaman."

msgid "The page slug (URL-friendly identifier)"
msgstr "Slug halaman (identifikasi ramah URL)"

msgid "Page content retrieved successfully"
msgstr "Konten halaman berhasil diambil"

msgid "Authentication required for this page"
msgstr "Otentikasi diperlukan untuk halaman ini"

msgid "Get legal/policy pages"
msgstr "Dapatkan halaman hukum/ketentuan"

msgid ""
"Get all legal and policy pages for footer navigation. Returns published "
"pages like Terms of Service, Privacy Policy, About Us, Contact, FAQ, Refund "
"Policy, and Shipping Policy. Useful for building site footers in headless "
"frontends."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua halaman hukum dan kebijakan untuk navigasi footer. "
"Mengembalikan halaman yang diterbitkan seperti Terms of Service, Privacy "
"Policy, About Us, Contact, FAQ, Refund Policy, dan Shipping Policy. Berguna "
"untuk membangun footer situs di frontend headless."

msgid "List of legal/policy pages"
msgstr "Daftar halaman hukum/ketentuan"

msgid "Get default page by type"
msgstr "Dapatkan halaman default berdasarkan tipe"

msgid ""
"Get the default page for a specific page type. Useful for headless frontends"
" to get the configured home page, category page template, cart page, "
"checkout page, etc. Returns the page marked as default for the type, or the "
"first published page of that type."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan halaman default untuk jenis halaman tertentu. Berguna untuk "
"frontend headless untuk mendapatkan halaman beranda yang dikonfigurasi, "
"template halaman kategori, halaman keranjang, halaman checkout, dll. "
"Mengembalikan halaman yang ditandai sebagai default untuk jenis tersebut, "
"atau halaman pertama yang diterbitkan dari jenis tersebut."

msgid ""
"Page type: home, category, product, cart, checkout, about, contact, or "
"custom"
msgstr ""
"Jenis halaman: home, kategori, produk, keranjang, checkout, tentang, kontak,"
" atau kustom"

msgid "Invalid page type"
msgstr "Jenis halaman tidak valid"

msgid "No page found for this type"
msgstr "Tidak ada halaman yang ditemukan untuk jenis ini"

msgid "List visibility rule groups"
msgstr "Grup Aturan Visibilitas Daftar"

msgid ""
"Get all active visibility rule groups for the visibility rules editor.\n"
"\n"
"    This endpoint returns saved rule groups that can be applied to page elements\n"
"    for advanced visibility conditions (e.g., show to US mobile users only,\n"
"    hide during business hours, show to VIP customers).\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only (requires login with staff privileges).\n"
"\n"
"    **Use cases:**\n"
"    - Populate saved rule groups dropdown in visibility rules editor\n"
"    - Allow staff to reuse pre-configured visibility conditions"
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua grup aturan visibilitas aktif untuk editor aturan visibilitas.\n"
"\n"
"Endpoint ini mengembalikan grup aturan yang disimpan yang dapat diterapkan pada elemen halaman\n"
"untuk kondisi visibilitas lanjutan (misalnya, tampilkan hanya untuk pengguna ponsel di AS,\n"
"sembunyikan selama jam kerja, tampilkan untuk pelanggan VIP).\n"
"\n"
"**Autentikasi:** Hanya staf (memerlukan login dengan hak akses staf).\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus penggunaan:**\n"
"- Mengisi dropdown grup aturan yang disimpan di editor aturan visibilitas\n"
"- Memungkinkan staf untuk memanfaatkan kembali kondisi visibilitas yang telah dikonfigurasikan sebelumnya"

msgid "List of active visibility rule groups"
msgstr "Daftar kelompok aturan visibilitas yang aktif"

msgid "Name is required"
msgstr "Nama diperlukan"

msgid "New Group"
msgstr "Kelompok Baru"

msgid "Invalid rule type"
msgstr "Jenis aturan tidak valid"

msgid "Get visibility rule types configuration"
msgstr "Dapatkan Konfigurasi Jenis Aturan Visibilitas"

msgid ""
"Returns configuration for all visibility rule types including operators\n"
"    and value input configurations. Used by the rule builder to dynamically\n"
"    render the rule editor.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only\n"
"\n"
"    **Response includes:**\n"
"    - Rule types organized by category (geo, user, device, time, etc.)\n"
"    - Operators with compatibility information\n"
"    - Value type configurations"
msgstr ""
"Mengembalikan konfigurasi untuk semua jenis aturan visibilitas termasuk operator\n"
"serta konfigurasi input nilai. Digunakan oleh pembuat aturan untuk merender editor aturan secara dinamis.\n"
"\n"
"**Autentikasi:** Hanya staf\n"
"\n"
"**Respons mencakup:**\n"
"- Jenis aturan yang dikelompokkan berdasarkan kategori (geo, user, device, time, dll.)\n"
"- Operator dengan informasi kompatibilitas\n"
"- Konfigurasi jenis nilai"

msgid "Rule types and operators configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Jenis Aturan dan Operator"

msgid "Get internal link sources"
msgstr "Dapatkan sumber tautan internal"

msgid ""
"Returns searchable internal content for link selector widgets.\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff only\n"
"\n"
"    **Query parameters:**\n"
"    - type: Filter by content type (all, product, page, category, blog)\n"
"    - search: Search term to filter results\n"
"    - limit: Max results per type (default: 10, max: 50)\n"
"\n"
"    **Response includes:**\n"
"    - Products, Pages, Categories, Blog Posts with URLs and thumbnails\n"
"    - URLs without language prefix for dynamic i18n"
msgstr ""
"Mengembalikan konten internal yang dapat dicari untuk widget pemilih tautan.\n"
"\n"
"**Autentikasi:** Hanya staf\n"
"\n"
"**Parameter pencarian:**\n"
"- jenis: Saring berdasarkan jenis konten (semua, produk, halaman, kategori, blog)\n"
"- cari: Kata kunci pencarian untuk menyaring hasil\n"
"- batas: Maksimal hasil per jenis (default: 10, maks: 50)\n"
"\n"
"**Respons mencakup:**\n"
"- Produk, Halaman, Kategori, Posting Blog dengan URL dan gambar mini\n"
"- URL tanpa awalan bahasa untuk i18n dinamis"

msgid "Content type filter"
msgstr "Penyaring Jenis Konten"

msgid "Search term"
msgstr "Kata Kunci Pencarian"

msgid "Max results per type"
msgstr "Maksimal hasil per tipe"

msgid "Link sources by content type"
msgstr "Sumber tautan berdasarkan tipe konten"

msgid "Page Builder"
msgstr "Pembangun Halaman"

